Gene.FullName: potassium voltage-gated channel modifier subfamily S member 3

SubmitterDescription.SubmitterName: International Standards For Cytogenomic Arrays Consortium (ISCA)

SampleDescription.Description: recombinent pericentric inversion. Phenotype: 46,XX,t(5;14)(q13;q32);inv(2)(p13q12), Cornelia de Lange similar dysmorphic features, short stature, fine motor delay, gross motor delay, learning disability, mild mental retardation, hypotonia since birth, joint hyperextensibility, gastroesophageal reflux, single kidney, imperforate hymen, parents with multiple miscarriages, mild deafness, maternal second degree male cousin with balanced translocation, learning disability and wife with multiple miscarriages
